896
01:27:09,126 --> 01:27:10,388
那些欢愉吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...pleasure?{\r}

897
01:27:28,779 --> 01:27:31,907
里海
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}{\r}

898
01:27:57,975 --> 01:27:59,033
在这儿等
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Wait here.{\r}

899
01:28:00,077 --> 01:28:01,305
真是多事之秋
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Always something.{\r}

900
01:28:01,545 --> 01:28:02,705
先是赌场
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}First the casino.{\r}

901
01:28:02,946 --> 01:28:04,743
现在是鱼子酱工厂
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Now the caviar factory.{\r}

902
01:28:04,948 --> 01:28:07,508
我是自由市场经济的奴隶
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I am a slave to the free-market economy.{\r}

903
01:28:24,134 --> 01:28:24,964
庞德还活着
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Bond is alive.{\r}

904
01:28:30,908 --> 01:28:33,206
这地方真是一团乱
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Is nothing in this place straight?{\r}

905
01:28:38,215 --> 01:28:39,512
你是谁？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Who are you?{\r}

906
01:28:40,117 --> 01:28:41,482
你是怎么进来的？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}And how did you get in?{\r}

907
01:28:42,119 --> 01:28:43,347
我要通知警卫
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I'll call security...{\r}

908
01:28:44,154 --> 01:28:46,315
好好地谢谢他们
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...and congratulate them.{\r}

909
01:28:46,657 --> 01:28:47,487
来一杯吧？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Drink?{\r}

910
01:28:50,928 --> 01:28:53,522
你不能像别人一样 打招呼吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Can't you say hello like a normal person?{\r}

911
01:28:55,199 --> 01:28:56,530
快走
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Get lost.{\r}

912
01:28:57,301 --> 01:28:59,895
不是啦,走后门
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}No, no, no. Down the back.{\r}

913
01:29:02,239 --> 01:29:03,900
你跟伊莉翠有什么来往？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}What's your business with Elektra?{\r}

914
01:29:04,808 --> 01:29:08,300
我以为你跟她才来电
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I thought you were the one giving her the business.{\r}

915
01:29:08,512 --> 01:29:11,879
她输给你一百万 好像理所当然
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}She drops $1 million in your casino, and you don't even blink.{\r}

916
01:29:12,115 --> 01:29:13,946
她为什么付钱给你？
