918
01:29:19,122 --> 01:29:20,384
不会有好下场
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...I wouldn't bet on it.{\r}

919
01:29:24,394 --> 01:29:26,885
五千元的鱼子酱泡汤了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}$5000 of beluga. Ruined.{\r}

920
01:29:27,097 --> 01:29:30,032
跟核弹比起来 这算不了什么
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}That's nothing compared to what a nuclear bomb can do.{\r}

921
01:29:30,934 --> 01:29:33,129
有一枚核弹遭窃
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}We had a nuclear bomb stolen this morning.{\r}

922
01:29:33,337 --> 01:29:35,669
雷纳跟伊莉翠是一伙的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Renard and Elektra King are working together.{\r}

923
01:29:35,873 --> 01:29:38,137
