924
01:32:01,752 --> 01:32:03,344
Q先生会被气炸
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Q's not gonna like this.{\r}

925
01:33:33,510 --> 01:33:34,340
出去！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Get out!{\r}

926
01:34:46,483 --> 01:34:47,279
救命啊！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Help!{\r}

927
01:34:47,517 --> 01:34:48,415
现在
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Now...{\r}

928
01:34:49,386 --> 01:34:50,318
我们讲到哪儿？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...where were we?{\r}

929
01:34:50,520 --> 01:34:52,511
-丢条绳子吧！ -不行,先说实话
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}-A rope, please! -No. The truth.{\r}

930
01:34:52,756 --> 01:34:53,723
她把M夫人抓走
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}She has M.{\r}

931
01:34:53,924 --> 01:34:57,087
-我不知情 -她想杀你灭口
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}-I know nothing. -Those blades were meant for you.{\r}

932
01:34:57,294 --> 01:34:59,660
为什么？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}What does Elektra King want you dead for?{\r}

933
01:34:59,930 --> 01:35:02,296
是你毁了我的工厂
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}It was you who destroyed my factory.{\r}

934
01:35:02,499 --> 01:35:04,433
是你把我的劳斯莱斯沉入湖底
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Then you drown my Rolls-Royce...{\r}

935
01:35:04,634 --> 01:35:08,126
你现在还想用鱼子酱把我淹死！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...and now you're trying to drown me in my own caviar!{\r}

936
01:35:08,338 --> 01:35:09,737
救我上去！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Let me out!{\r}

937
01:35:10,173 --> 01:35:13,336
可惜这儿没有香槟
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Too bad we don't have any champagne.{\r}

938
01:35:13,543 --> 01:35:14,805
或是酸奶
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Or sour cream.{\r}

939
01:35:17,714 --> 01:35:19,011
偶尔
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Occasionally...{\r}

940
01:35:19,683 --> 01:35:22,982
我会替她弄到俄制的器材
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...I get equipment for her. Machinery. Russian stuff.{\r}

941
01:35:23,854 --> 01:35:25,583
赌场的一百万呢？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}And the payoff in the casino?{\r}

942
01:35:26,089 --> 01:35:27,317
那是特别差事
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}It was a special job.{\r}

943
01:35:28,124 --> 01:35:30,115
我侄子是海军
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}My nephew is in the navy.{\r}

944
01:35:31,194 --> 01:35:34,391
他替她走私一些机器
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}He's smuggling some machinery for her.{\r}

945
01:35:34,598 --> 01:35:36,429
-在哪儿？ -我不能说
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}-Where? -Absolutely not!{\r}

946
01:35:36,633 --> 01:35:37,657
哪儿？！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Where?!{\r}

947
01:35:41,037 --> 01:35:43,198
-哪儿？ -伊斯坦堡！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}-Where? -Istanbul!{\r}

948
01:35:52,849 --> 01:35:53,645
你！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}You!{\r}

949
01:35:53,884 --> 01:35:56,250
这金牙猴王 跑哪儿去了？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Where have you been, you gold-encrusted buffoon?{\r}

950
01:35:56,453 --> 01:35:59,183
抱歉,我被撞昏了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Sorry, boss. I must have bumped my head.{\r}

951
01:35:59,389 --> 01:36:02,881
把我救出来 我会让你知道什么是撞昏
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Get me out of here, I'll show you what a bumped head feels like.{\r}

952
01:36:03,660 --> 01:36:04,752
瞧
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Look.{\r}

953
01:36:04,961 --> 01:36:08,397
屋顶没了至少墙壁还在
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}We have no roof, but at least we have four good walls.{\r}

954
01:36:20,377 --> 01:36:24,336
保险公司一定会抓狂
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}The insurance company is never going to believe this.{\r}

955
01:37:25,709 --> 01:37:29,941
这里以前是KGB的分部
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}This used to be the KGB's Istanbul safe house. Now it's FSB.{\r}

956
01:37:30,146 --> 01:37:31,909
现在是联邦安全局
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Federal Security Bureau.{\r}

957
01:37:32,115 --> 01:37:34,743
其实是换汤不换药
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Same old friendly service with a new name.{\r}

958
01:37:35,352 --> 01:37:37,252
-找到尼可莱吗？ -没有
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}-Did you raise Nikoli? -Nothing.{\r}

959
01:37:37,454 --> 01:37:39,979
试着扫描紧急讯号
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Try scanning the emergency frequencies.{\r}

960
01:37:41,725 --> 01:37:42,783
可怜哪
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Tragedy.{\r}

961
01:37:43,293 --> 01:37:45,693
以前至少有一百个地方
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}In the old days, there were 1 00 places...{\r}

962
01:37:45,895 --> 01:37:48,329
能让潜艇偷偷升到水面
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...where a submarine could surface undetected.{\r}

963
01:37:48,531 --> 01:37:49,361
潜艇？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Submarine?{\r}

964
01:37:50,333 --> 01:37:52,301
你侄子的潜艇是什么型号？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}What class is your nephew running?{\r}

965
01:37:53,203 --> 01:37:55,364
你们称之为维特3型
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Victor 3, you call it.{\r}

966
01:37:55,572 --> 01:37:59,030
核能潜艇 他们要用潜艇的核子反应炉
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Nuclear. He's not loading cargo. They want the sub to use the reactor.{\r}

967
01:37:59,242 --> 01:38:00,072
没错
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}That's it.{\r}

968
01:38:00,276 --> 01:38:03,211
把钸元素放进核子反应炉
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Put weapons-grade plutonium in that sub's reactor...{\r}

969
01:38:03,413 --> 01:38:05,779
就会造成严重的核爆
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...instant, catastrophic meltdown.{\r}

970
01:38:05,982 --> 01:38:08,746
看起来像是场意外
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Making it all look just like an accident.{\r}

971
01:38:08,985 --> 01:38:10,179
为什么？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}But why?{\r}

972
01:38:10,687 --> 01:38:14,123
里海的输油管
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Because the existing pipelines from the Caspian Sea...{\r}

973
01:38:14,357 --> 01:38:16,882
把石油运到北部
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...go to the north. Here.{\r}

974
01:38:17,093 --> 01:38:21,291
这里,再用油轮从黑海 运到伊斯坦堡
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}The oil is put on the tankers, shipped across the Black Sea to Istanbul.{\r}

975
01:38:21,798 --> 01:38:24,130
核爆会摧毁伊斯坦堡
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}The explosion would destroy Istanbul...{\r}

976
01:38:24,834 --> 01:38:27,462
污染整个博斯普鲁斯海峡几十年
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...contaminating the Bosporus for decades.{\r}

977
01:38:28,204 --> 01:38:30,331
这样一来 只有一个方法能输出石油
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}There'd be one way to get the oil out.{\r}

978
01:38:30,540 --> 01:38:32,940
从南边到地中海
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Down south to the Med.{\r}

979
01:38:33,143 --> 01:38:34,474
金恩输油管
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}The King pipeline.{\r}

980
01:38:35,078 --> 01:38:36,170
伊莉翠的输油管
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Elektra's pipeline.{\r}

981
01:38:36,379 --> 01:38:38,142
一定要找到尼克莱
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}We must find Nikoli.{\r}

982
01:38:39,983 --> 01:38:41,382
尼克莱舰长？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Captain Nikoli?{\r}

983
01:38:43,486 --> 01:38:44,384
你好
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Sir.{\r}

984
01:38:45,522 --> 01:38:47,046
准备装货了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Ready to load your cargo.{\r}

985
01:38:47,290 --> 01:38:50,453
-我们只有几个小时 -你用最少的人员？
