986
01:38:50,660 --> 01:38:52,685
-我们付不起太多人 -当然了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}-That's all we can afford. -Of course.{\r}

987
01:38:53,096 --> 01:38:55,394
给弟兄们的白兰地和点心
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Some brandy and refreshments for your men.{\r}

988
01:38:57,400 --> 01:38:58,492
谢谢你
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Thank you.{\r}

989
01:39:03,773 --> 01:39:04,705
早安
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Good morning.{\r}

990
01:39:09,546 --> 01:39:10,877
什么时候了？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}What's the time?{\r}

991
01:39:24,494 --> 01:39:26,428
你的死期到了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}It's time for you to die.{\r}

992
01:39:58,995 --> 01:40:00,428
我收到讯号
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I've got something.{\r}

993
01:40:01,364 --> 01:40:03,127
在紧急频道上
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}On the emergency frequency.{\r}

994
01:40:03,333 --> 01:40:05,927
每十五秒发出两组六位数号码
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Two six-digit numbers cycled every 1 5 seconds.{\r}

995
01:40:06,136 --> 01:40:08,001
