{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}A GPS signal. Position coordinates.{\r}

996
01:40:08,204 --> 01:40:10,069
核弹晶片,M夫人
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Locator card. M.{\r}

997
01:40:13,476 --> 01:40:14,943
-这儿 -处女塔
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}-Here. -Maiden's Tower.{\r}

998
01:40:15,445 --> 01:40:16,673
你去过吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Have you been there?{\r}

999
01:40:17,147 --> 01:40:18,136
没有,蛮牛
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}No. Mr. Bullion.{\r}

1000
01:40:22,318 --> 01:40:23,376
有炸弹！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Bomb!{\r}

1001
01:40:30,326 --> 01:40:31,759
快走
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Come on, come on.{\r}

1002
01:40:45,575 --> 01:40:46,872
你先请
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}After you.{\r}

1003
01:40:47,610 --> 01:40:49,043
我坚持
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I insist.{\r}

1004
01:41:05,995 --> 01:41:07,895
最后的晚餐好吃吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Enjoyed your meal, boys?{\r}

1005
01:41:15,772 --> 01:41:17,899
把他们丢进海里喂鱼
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Take them up and throw them in the sea.{\r}

1006
01:41:30,186 --> 01:41:31,312
反应炉在里面
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}The extruder's in here.{\r}

1007
01:41:33,223 --> 01:41:37,182
我得花半小时做成钸元素棒
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}It'll take half an hour to set up the machine to make the plutonium rod.{\r}

1008
01:41:44,033 --> 01:41:45,432
把他们带进来
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Put them in here.{\r}

1009
01:41:55,011 --> 01:41:56,740
反应炉没问题
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}The reactor is secured.{\r}

1010
01:41:56,980 --> 01:41:58,971
一切都照计划进行
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Everything is complete as planned.{\r}

1011
01:42:01,384 --> 01:42:05,150
-直升机来了吗？ -半小时后会来接我
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}-Is your helicopter ready? -It'll pick me up in half an hour.{\r}

1012
01:42:08,658 --> 01:42:10,182
这就是结局了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Then this is the end.{\r}

1013
01:42:12,228 --> 01:42:13,786
不,这是开始
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}This is the beginning.{\r}

1014
01:42:14,864 --> 01:42:17,264
世界将全面改观
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}The world will never be the same.{\r}

1015
01:42:30,246 --> 01:42:31,736
未来在你手中
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}The future is yours.{\r}

1016
01:42:33,583 --> 01:42:34,914
好好地玩吧
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Have fun with it.{\r}

1017
01:42:51,868 --> 01:42:53,096
要是你不来搅局
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}If you'd kept away...{\r}

1018
01:42:53,303 --> 01:42:56,704
也许哪天我们真的能相爱
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...we might've met in a few years and become lovers once more.{\r}

1019
01:43:06,282 --> 01:43:07,214
把她押去雷纳那儿
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Take her to Renard.{\r}

1020
01:43:10,586 --> 01:43:12,019
她好漂亮
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Pretty thing.{\r}

1021
01:43:12,989 --> 01:43:14,479
你也上过她？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}You had her too?{\r}

1022
01:43:19,262 --> 01:43:21,127
我能让你称霸天下
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I could've given you the world.{\r}

1023
01:43:22,598 --> 01:43:24,190
我绝不贪得无厌
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}The world is not enough.{\r}

1024
01:43:25,101 --> 01:43:26,500
你真傻
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Foolish sentiment.{\r}

1025
01:43:27,170 --> 01:43:28,694
这是我家族的座右铭
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Family motto.{\r}

1026
01:43:31,474 --> 01:43:35,843
考古学家在这里 挖出很多古董花瓶
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}They were digging near here, and they found some very pretty vases.{\r}

1027
01:43:37,113 --> 01:43:39,240
还找到这张椅子
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}They also found this chair.{\r}

1028
01:43:49,959 --> 01:43:52,894
现代人都不会念旧
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I think we ignore the old ways at our peril...{\r}

1029
01:43:53,096 --> 01:43:54,358
对吧？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...don't you?{\r}

1030
01:43:54,897 --> 01:43:56,125
M夫人呢？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Where's M?{\r}

1031
01:43:56,632 --> 01:43:58,497
她就快粉身碎骨了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Soon she'll be everywhere.{\r}

1032
01:44:00,136 --> 01:44:01,034
你这么做
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}All this...{\r}

1033
01:44:02,805 --> 01:44:05,069
因为你爱上雷纳？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...because you fell for Renard?{\r}

1034
01:44:08,044 --> 01:44:11,013
再转五下你的脖子 就会被绞断
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Five more turns and your neck will break.{\r}

1035
01:44:14,684 --> 01:44:17,152
我一向都很会玩弄男人
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I've always had a power over men.{\r}

1036
01:44:19,188 --> 01:44:23,522
当我知道我父亲不付赎金
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}When I realized my father wouldn't rescue me from the kidnappers...{\r}

1037
01:44:23,926 --> 01:44:26,588
我就得跟绑匪结盟
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...I knew I had to form another alliance.{\r}

1038
01:44:28,064 --> 01:44:29,156
你
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}You...{\r}

1039
01:44:30,166 --> 01:44:31,895
把雷纳玩弄于股掌
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...turned Renard.{\r}

1040
01:44:33,169 --> 01:44:34,761
我也玩弄了你
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Just like you...{\r}

1041
01:44:35,004 --> 01:44:37,905
只是你更容易玩弄
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...only you were even easier.{\r}

1042
01:44:41,477 --> 01:44:43,138
我叫他真的动手伤我
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I told him he had to hurt me.{\r}

1043
01:44:43,913 --> 01:44:46,006
看起来一定要像真的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}He had to make it look real.{\r}

1044
01:44:46,849 --> 01:44:47,747
他不肯
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}When he refused...{\r}

1045
01:44:49,218 --> 01:44:52,415
我就说我自己来
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...I told him I would do it myself.{\r}

1046
01:44:58,027 --> 01:44:59,892
你杀死了你父亲
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}So you killed your father.{\r}

1047
01:45:00,863 --> 01:45:02,091
是他先杀了我
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}He killed me.{\r}

1048
01:45:03,933 --> 01:45:06,265
他不肯付赎金就是杀了我
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}He killed me the day he refused to pay my ransom.{\r}

1049
01:45:06,469 --> 01:45:08,733
你全是为了石油吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Was this all about the oil?{\r}

1050
01:45:10,306 --> 01:45:12,103
那是我的石油
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}It is my oil.{\r}

1051
01:45:12,942 --> 01:45:13,909
我
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Mine...{\r}

1052
01:45:14,110 --> 01:45:15,475
和我家族的石油
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...and my family's.{\r}

1053
01:45:15,678 --> 01:45:18,806
流在我的血液里 比血还浓
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}It runs in my veins, thicker than blood.{\r}

1054
01:45:20,083 --> 01:45:22,483
我要重新整合天下
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm going to redraw the map.{\r}

1055
01:45:22,719 --> 01:45:26,018
当我完成后 整个世界都会知道我
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}And when I'm through, the whole world will know my name...{\r}

1056
01:45:26,222 --> 01:45:29,487
和我外公的名字 我的族人的荣耀！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...my grandfather's name, the glory of my people!{\r}

1057
01:45:29,692 --> 01:45:33,219
没有人会相信核爆是场意外
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}No one will believe this meltdown was an accident.{\r}

1058
01:45:33,429 --> 01:45:35,158
他们一定会相信的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}They will all believe.{\r}

1059
01:45:36,666 --> 01:45:38,293
你明白吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}You understand?{\r}

1060
01:45:38,735 --> 01:45:40,635
没有人能抗拒我
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Nobody can resist me.{\r}

1061
01:45:45,441 --> 01:45:48,467
你知道被绞死的感觉吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}You know what happens when a man is strangled?{\r}

1062
01:45:50,613 --> 01:45:52,478
现在还不迟
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}It's not too late.{\r}

1063
01:45:53,850 --> 01:45:56,580
不必害死八百万人
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Eight million people need not die.{\r}

1064
01:45:58,421 --> 01:46:01,083
你有机会时应该杀了我
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}You should've killed me when you had the chance.{\r}

1065
01:46:02,191 --> 01:46:03,852
但你下不了手 无法对我下手
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}But you couldn't. Not me.{\r}

1066
01:46:04,060 --> 01:46:05,891
无法对你心爱的女人下手
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Not a woman you've loved.{\r}

1067
01:46:15,972 --> 01:46:18,463
我对你毫无感情
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}You meant nothing to me.{\r}

1068
01:46:23,746 --> 01:46:24,576
再
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}One...{\r}

1069
01:46:26,015 --> 01:46:27,141
转
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...last...{\r}

1070
01:46:29,152 --> 01:46:30,551
最后一下
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...screw.{\r}

1071
01:46:54,911 --> 01:46:55,741
老板
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Boss...{\r}

1072
01:46:56,813 --> 01:46:57,905
你没死
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...you're alive.{\r}

1073
01:46:58,114 --> 01:46:59,376
见到你真好
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}So glad to see you.{\r}

1074
01:47:00,416 --> 01:47:01,508
我也一样
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Me too.{\r}

1075
01:47:07,557 --> 01:47:08,819
我在找一艘潜艇
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm looking for a sub.{\r}

1076
01:47:09,025 --> 01:47:12,256
一艘大大黑黑的 舰长是我老朋友
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}It's big and black, and the driver is a good friend of mine.{\r}

1077
01:47:17,500 --> 01:47:19,434
带我去找他
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Bring it to me.{\r}

1078
01:47:20,737 --> 01:47:21,863
可惜
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}What a shame.{\r}

1079
01:47:22,372 --> 01:47:23,634
他刚走不久
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}He's just gone.{\r}

1080
01:48:11,521 --> 01:48:13,580
他真的痛恨你
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Zukovsky really hated you.{\r}

1081
01:48:15,858 --> 01:48:18,554
没问题了 你好了吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Everything's under control up here. Are you ready?{\r}

1082
01:48:25,468 --> 01:48:27,095
好了,该说晚安了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Time to say good night.{\r}

1083
01:48:56,666 --> 01:48:57,997
你不会冷血地
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}You can't kill me.{\r}

1084
01:48:58,201 --> 01:48:59,725
杀我
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Not in cold blood.{\r}

1085
01:49:29,298 --> 01:49:30,390
阻止他
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Call him off.{\r}

1086
01:49:37,540 --> 01:49:39,098
我不想再说一次
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I won't ask again.{\r}

1087
01:49:40,443 --> 01:49:41,808
阻止他
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Call him off.{\r}

1088
01:49:43,312 --> 01:49:44,574
快阻止他！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Call him off!{\r}

1089
01:49:54,857 --> 01:49:56,449
你下不了手
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}You wouldn't kill me.{\r}

1090
01:49:57,159 --> 01:49:58,490
你没这么狠心
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}You'd miss me.{\r}

1091
01:50:02,665 --> 01:50:03,757
快下潜！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Dive! Bond--{\r}

1092
01:50:10,172 --> 01:50:11,503
我绝不心软
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I never miss.{\r}

1093
01:51:19,742 --> 01:51:21,004
她人呢？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Where is she?{\r}

1094
01:51:40,796 --> 01:51:42,024
以为我忘了？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Thought I'd forgotten?{\r}

1095
01:52:15,264 --> 01:52:17,198
下潜一百英尺后直航
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Level at 1 00 feet.{\r}

1096
01:52:17,633 --> 01:52:19,100
稳住了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Hold her steady.{\r}

1097
01:52:29,445 --> 01:52:30,742
一百英尺
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Level at 1 00 feet.{\r}

1098
01:52:36,185 --> 01:52:38,619
只要逼他们浮出水面
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}If we can force them up to the surface...{\r}

1099
01:52:38,821 --> 01:52:40,686
潜艇会被间谍卫星发现
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...they'll show up on the spy satellite...{\r}

1100
01:52:41,057 --> 01:52:42,524
海军就会赶来
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...bring out the navy.{\r}

1101
01:52:53,169 --> 01:52:54,636
快,起来！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Come on. Get up!{\r}

1102
01:52:54,837 --> 01:52:55,929
快走！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Over there. Move!{\r}

1103
01:52:56,372 --> 01:52:57,600
给我过去！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Move! Go, go!{\r}

1104
01:52:57,807 --> 01:52:58,865
过去！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Get over there!{\r}

1105
01:52:59,075 --> 01:53:00,337
别乱动！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Stay!{\r}

1106
01:53:00,543 --> 01:53:01,373
手举起来！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Up!{\r}

1107
01:53:31,540 --> 01:53:34,008
拉平！拉平了！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Get us level! Level!{\r}

1108
01:53:34,210 --> 01:53:35,837
全被打烂了！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}It's all smashed!{\r}

1109
01:53:36,045 --> 01:53:37,103
克莉莫丝？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Christmas?{\r}

1110
01:53:38,581 --> 01:53:40,048
我们应该笔直上升？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}So we're going up then?{\r}

1111
01:53:40,549 --> 01:53:42,278
我稍微算错了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Slight miscalculation.{\r}

1112
01:53:54,396 --> 01:53:55,488
抓紧了！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Hold on!{\r}

1113
01:53:57,633 --> 01:53:59,567
千万要抓紧
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Hold on, hold on.{\r}

1114
01:54:14,884 --> 01:54:16,249
小心了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Brace yourself.{\r}

1115
01:54:45,481 --> 01:54:46,675
进水了！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}It's flooding!{\r}

1116
01:54:47,416 --> 01:54:49,043
快爬到上面去
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Get up to the hatch.{\r}

1117
01:54:56,625 --> 01:54:58,354
快点！快！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Damn! Come on!{\r}

1118
01:54:59,161 --> 01:55:00,389
快！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Go, go!{\r}

1119
01:55:25,521 --> 01:55:27,785
他启动反应炉！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}He's opened up the reactor!{\r}

1120
01:55:28,090 --> 01:55:29,682
把自己锁在里面
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}And locked himself in!{\r}

1121
01:55:29,892 --> 01:55:31,757
我得去找他
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I have to get up there to him.{\r}

1122
01:55:32,228 --> 01:55:33,286
我们只有一次机会
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}We have one chance.{\r}

1123
01:55:33,762 --> 01:55:38,358
我要游到外面 再从逃生舱口进入反应炉室
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I'll get out and back in through the reactor room escape hatch.{\r}

1124
01:55:41,971 --> 01:55:45,930
红灯一亮 就按下去让我进去
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}When the light goes red, press this button so I can get back in.{\r}

1125
01:55:46,609 --> 01:55:48,076
这太危险了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}James, it's too risky.{\r}

1126
01:55:48,277 --> 01:55:49,539
要是我失败
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}If I don't make it...{\r}

1127
01:55:49,745 --> 01:55:52,236
你就从这里逃生 关上舱门
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...use this chamber to get out. Close the hatch.{\r}

1128
01:55:52,448 --> 01:55:54,177
一路要吐气 关起来
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Exhale all the way up. Close it.{\r}

1129
01:58:27,403 --> 01:58:28,392
救命啊！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Help!{\r}

1130
01:58:39,515 --> 01:58:40,709
快点！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Come on, come on!{\r}

1131
01:58:44,019 --> 01:58:45,884
只要反应炉不爆炸
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}We're safe from the radiation...{\r}

1132
01:58:46,088 --> 01:58:48,318
我们就没有辐射线的危险
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...if the reactor coolant doesn't burst.{\r}

1133
01:58:49,058 --> 01:58:51,754
要是他把钸元素插进去
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}If he had gotten the plutonium rod in the reactor...{\r}

1134
01:58:51,960 --> 01:58:54,326
伊斯坦堡就完了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}...we could've written off the whole city.{\r}

1135
01:58:58,567 --> 01:59:00,501
欢迎加入我的核子家族
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Welcome to my nuclear family.{\r}

1136
01:59:27,162 --> 01:59:29,630
你真的愿意为她死吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Are you really gonna commit suicide for her?{\r}

1137
01:59:29,832 --> 01:59:32,232
你忘了,我早就死了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}You forget, I'm already dead.{\r}

1138
01:59:32,534 --> 01:59:33,466
你没听说吗？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Haven't you heard?{\r}

1139
01:59:34,603 --> 01:59:36,036
她也死了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}So is she.{\r}

1140
01:59:39,641 --> 01:59:40,573
你在说谎
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}You're lying.{\r}

1141
01:59:42,244 --> 01:59:43,768
骗子！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Liar!{\r}

1142
01:59:45,481 --> 01:59:46,607
骗子！
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Liar!{\r}

1143
02:01:08,830 --> 02:01:10,229
她在地狱等你
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}She's waiting for you.{\r}

1144
02:01:28,684 --> 02:01:30,584
氢气指数过高
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}The hydrogen gas level's too high.{\r}

1145
02:01:31,320 --> 02:01:33,481
只要稍微有一点火花 反应炉就会爆炸
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}One spark and the reactor'll blow.{\r}

1146
02:01:33,722 --> 02:01:35,280
我得想办法阻止
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}I have to stop it.{\r}

1147
02:01:38,961 --> 02:01:41,759
到上面的鱼雷发射孔等我
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}Go to the top of the sub. Meet me in the torpedo bay.{\r}

1148
02:01:48,070 --> 02:01:49,594
反应炉进水了
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}The reactor is flooded.{\r}

1149
02:01:51,473 --> 02:01:54,135
就算爆炸也不会有危险
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H00FFFF&}So it's safe even if this place blows.{\r}

1150
02:02:38,287 --> 02:02:40,016
不,这样不行
